{"tid":752463,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"以現今嘅市價，從前全盛時期的球星球王球皇依家轉會值幾多錢？","createTime":"2018-07-22T23:34:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-23T03:42:40.000Z","uid":125305,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7e34787591570706bc7f4d8eace9301d5946b13d","tid":752463,"uid":125305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T23:34:09.000Z","msg":"舉個例子，全盛阿朗當時賣80m，放今年我覺得值300m（最少高過屁馬）<br />\n當年保方賣52m，今年賣應該最少都130m以上。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n近幾年先轉嘅如果覺得今年買會唔同都可以提出。<br />\n例如我自己今年買就應該可以去到130~150m。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歡迎理性討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"705d95ecb3f186a05bbb375abf493d43ad11434f","tid":752463,"uid":2267,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T23:49:24.000Z","msg":"9號號朗拿度：10000000M<br />\n朗拿癲佬（奴）：1000000000000M"},{"pid":"a8df3ea2cce8b3d98eb188582ff56c827c46a8bf","tid":752463,"uid":96941,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"705d95ecb3f186a05bbb375abf493d43ad11434f","tid":752463,"uid":2267,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T23:49:24.000Z","msg":"9號號朗拿度：10000000M<br />\n朗拿癲佬（奴）：1000000000000M"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T23:53:41.000Z","msg":"得紫靈老豆先買得起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0da8a4c98dfa2d6d1fcc5211a861846964a7fe6a","tid":752463,"uid":158933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T02:40:28.000Z","msg":"當時CR7既80m依加顯得好少咁，但其實當年嚟講，真係好撚痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eedcc67e645829eb23069c7974518baaea2f75da","tid":752463,"uid":47470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T03:03:23.000Z","msg":"從結果黎睇 c7 保方一買可以用十幾年唔洗買人，仲要係十幾年超勁水平<br />\n300m都算係抵到爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68981872437b4712aefb083f33cac84b7c0f6f58","ti